## 1. Definitions

**“Source Code”** refers to all code files in this repository, including JavaScript, TypeScript, JSX/TSX, CSS, configuration files, build files, and related scripts, written by the project authors.

**“Project Content”** refers to the textual, visual, and descriptive material created specifically for this website, including but not limited to:
school descriptions, history, article texts, program explanations, and any embedded written content produced by the project authors.

**“Third-Party Assets”** refers to images, icons, fonts, libraries, or other resources sourced from external providers that include their own licenses.
These assets **are not covered by this license**, and retain the license terms set by their original creators.

